com.net2plan.libraries

Class WDMUtils.LightpathAdd

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.net2plan.libraries.WDMUtils.LightpathAdd
  • Enclosing class:
    WDMUtils

    public static class WDMUtils.LightpathAdd
extends Object
    This class represents the request to add a new lightpath. It is used in online algorithms related to WDM networks, inside SimEvent objects.
